<msbt attribsize="4">
	<message label="DiveFish_02620" attrib="00 00 00 00"><colour id="1" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />裙帶菜<colour id="65535" />呢，<delay frames="30" />是一種分布在日本近海的海藻，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />生命週期為一年。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />它在海裡是茶色的，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但只要經過加熱，<delay20 />就會變成鮮豔的綠色。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在日本和朝鮮半島等地區，自古以來<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是一種非常普遍的食材。<pageBreak /><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，由於在全世界大量繁殖，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對生態系統造成不好的影響，<delay20 />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因此被視為外來入侵物種，<delay8 />不受歡迎呢<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="DiveFish_02830" attrib="00 00 00 00"><colour id="1" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />海葡萄<colour id="65535" />是一種礦物質豐富的海藻。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />擁有爽脆彈牙的口感，<delay8 />
吃的時候<delay20 />可以感受到大海的風味。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其真正的名字是「長莖葡萄蕨藻」，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過因為「海葡萄」比較好記，<delay8 />
所以還是這個名字<delay20 />較為有名呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />由於在低溫下會失去爽脆的口感，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以還是不要保存在冰箱裡比較好喔。</message>
	<message label="DiveFish_02831" attrib="00 00 00 00"><colour id="1" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />海膽<colour id="65535" /><delay20 />是海星跟海參的近親。
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />別看牠那樣，牠可是能走路的喔。<delay20 />
牠會從尖刺之間伸出細長的腳來移動。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聽說還會使用身體下方的嘴<delay8 />
來吃海藻等生物，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且咀嚼力還滿強的。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="1" />海膽<colour id="65535" />的天敵除了海星，<delay20 />條石鯛和河豚也
毫不在意牠身上的尖刺，<delay8 /><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />把牠當成佳餚呢。<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay20 />還有<delay8 /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />海獺也是<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="DiveFish_02832" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />附著在岩石上的<colour id="1" />藤壺<colour id="65535" />，<delay frames="30" />乍看之下是貝類，<delay8 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實是蝦子和螃蟹的同類，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />味道也跟螃蟹類似。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />剛出生的<colour id="1" />藤壺<colour id="65535" />沒有殼，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />會像蝦子一樣在海裡漂浮。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />附著到岩石上以後，<delay20 />
殼會隨著時間慢慢成形，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />長成我們所知道的<colour id="1" />藤壺<colour id="65535" />喔。</message>
	<message label="DiveFish_02833" attrib="00 00 00 00"><colour id="1" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />牡蠣<colour id="65535" /><delay20 />被稱為「海中牛奶」，<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是營養價值非常高的雙殼貝類。<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />牡蠣只會在出生後兩到三週的<delay8 />幼年期游泳，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一旦附著到岩石上，<delay8 />就幾乎不會動，<delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />並在那個地方生活一輩子。</message>
	<message label="DiveFish_02834" attrib="00 00 00 00"><colour id="1" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />角蠑螺<colour id="65535" />主要棲息在岩石較多的海邊，<delay8 />
是螺的同類。<delay frames="30" /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />貝殼的開口處有一個蓋子，<delay8 />
移動時，<delay20 />會把蓋子收到殼裡。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />夜晚的活動力較旺盛，<delay8 />會在岩石上移動，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />並以裙帶菜等海藻為食。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有的個體殼上有角，有的則沒有。<delay frames="30" />
雖然有角的個體大多生長在波濤洶湧的海域，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但兩者之間的因果關係尚未釐清呢。</message>
	<message label="DiveFish_02835" attrib="00 00 00 00"><colour id="1" /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />鮑魚<colour id="65535" />乍看之下是單殼貝類，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但其實是螺的同類。<delay frames="30" /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要仔細觀察外殼，<delay8 />
就會發現其頂端的螺旋紋。<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />由於鮑魚一年只生長2公分，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因此要經過漫長的歲月才能長成大鮑魚。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />鮑魚的營養價值高<delay8 />又有嚼勁，<delay frames="30" />
經常用於鐵板或清蒸料理中，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是高級料理中相當知名的食材。<delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="DiveFish_02838" attrib="00 00 00 00"><colour id="1" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />珠母蛤<colour id="65535" /><delay8 />是一種被稱為珍珠貝的雙殼貝類，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />會分泌蛋白質等物質，<delay8 />
將進入殼中的異物包裹起來，<delay20 />形成珍珠。<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還會從殼的縫隙間伸出好幾根細絲般的腳，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />附著在岩石<delay8 />或周圍的同類身上生活。</message>
	<message label="DiveFish_02839" attrib="00 00 00 00"><colour id="1" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />帆立貝<colour id="65535" /><delay20 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />棲息在冰冷的海底沙地。
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在生長到一定大小後，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />貝殼就會動起來，<delay8 />用力吐出海水來游泳。<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />邊緣較輕薄的部分<delay8 />被稱為「裙邊」，<delay20 />
<anim id="Shaking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />上面有超過80個黑點，<delay8 />是帆立貝的眼睛。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖說是眼睛，但只能勉強感受光線而已。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大大的貝柱可以用奶油烤來吃，<delay20 />
而貝殼也能拿來作為焗烤的容器，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不論味道還是外觀，<delay20 />都能感受到大海的恩賜。</message>
	<message label="DiveFish_02840" attrib="00 00 00 00"><colour id="1" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />海葵<colour id="65535" /><delay8 />會附著在海底的岩石或珊瑚上，<delay20 />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />利用搖曳的有毒觸手，<delay8 />將靠過來的
魚蝦刺起來，<delay20 />等到牠們動彈不得之後再吃掉。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然說是有毒，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是大部分對人體沒有影響。<pageBreak /><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過當中也有較強的毒素，<delay20 />
會引起劇烈疼痛，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以還是不要隨便觸碰比較好喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />另外，這個<colour id="1" />海葵<colour id="65535" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />似乎跟小丑魚是好朋友呢<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="DiveFish_02841" attrib="00 00 00 00"><colour id="1" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />海星<colour id="65535" />的觸手<delay8 />呈星形展開，能自由地活動。<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />靠著觸手上長出的數隻小腳<delay8 />便能緩慢移動，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />此外，還能用觸手撬開貝殼來吃。<delay20 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是觸手被敵人抓住了，<delay8 />就會切斷觸手逃走。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為再生能力很強，很快就會再長出來。<pageBreak /><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還有些種類會將胃從嘴裡吐出來，<delay20 />
纏住獵物直接消化，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這種進食方式真是奇怪啊。</message>
	<message label="DiveFish_02842" attrib="00 00 00 00"><colour id="1" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />海參<colour id="65535" /><delay8 />是一種與海膽和海星相近的生物，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />牠們都同樣沒有心臟和腦部。<delay20 />而不同的是，
海參的身體表面沒有尖刺或殼，<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />非常柔軟。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果遇到敵人，<delay20 /><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />海參會從尾部
噴出絲狀的黏液把敵人纏住，<delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓對方無法活動。<pageBreak /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />當中也有一些海參會冒著生命危險，<delay20 />
將自己的內臟吐出來，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />趁敵人在吃的時候逃走。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那些內臟<delay8 />只要花1到3個月就會再生，<delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />恢復成原來的模樣呢<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="DiveFish_02843" attrib="00 00 00 00"><colour id="1" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />海蛞蝓<colour id="65535" />是螺的同類。<10_4 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />牠們的貝殼有的退化了，<delay8 />有的變小了，<delay8 />
有的則是埋在體內看不見。<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其鮮艷的色彩、花紋、<delay20 />形狀和大小
變化多端，拍起照來十分好看，<delay frames="30" />
所以很受潛水者的歡迎喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />由於不同的種類，<delay8 />只會吃特定的食物，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以飼養起來非常困難。</message>
	<message label="DiveFish_02844" attrib="00 00 00 00"><colour id="1" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />海扁蟲<colour id="65535" />名副其實，<delay20 />
是一種扁平的海洋生物。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有些種類像海蛞蝓一樣<delay8 />擁有漂亮的花紋，<delay20 />
但其實牠們是兩種完全不同的生物呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />當中也有些種類帶有毒性，<delay20 />
成分跟河豚的毒相同，是一種劇毒，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以一定要小心留意喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />別看<colour id="1" />海扁蟲<colour id="65535" />那個樣子，其實牠是非常凶悍的，<delay20 />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有些甚至會利用自己扁平的特性，<delay20 />
從貝殼的縫隙鑽進去，<delay20 />吃掉裡面的肉呢。<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="DiveFish_02845" attrib="00 00 00 00"><colour id="1" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />蝦蛄<colour id="65535" /><delay8 />看起來是蝦子的同類，<delay frames="30" /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但在分類上
卻屬於其他物種，<delay20 />兩者是遠房親戚。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />牠的前腳如鐮刀般巨大，<delay20 />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />身上包覆著帶有尖刺的鎧甲，<delay8 />
樣子十分威武。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />牠會用鐮刀般的前腳敲擊捕捉到的獵物，<delay8 />
有人稱之為「蝦蛄拳」。<delay frames="30" />而「蝦蛄拳」十分
強而有力，據說連螃蟹殼<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />都能輕鬆敲碎呢。<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="DiveFish_02846" attrib="00 00 00 00"><colour id="1" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />甜蝦<colour id="65535" />其實是俗稱，<delay frames="30" />其真正的名字是
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「北國紅蝦」，<delay20 />
是一種棲息在北方深海海域的蝦子。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />出生三年左右的甜蝦，沒有性別之分，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />到了第四～五年，會全部轉換性別為雄性，<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等到交配後的第五～六年，又會轉為雌性。<delay20 />
這種生態現象<delay8 />真的是相當稀有啊。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="DiveFish_02847" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說到蝦子，<delay20 />會聯想到<colour id="1" /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />日本囊對蝦<colour id="65535" />的人
也不算少數呢。<delay20 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />牠可說是<delay20 />具有代表性的蝦子。<10_4 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />煮熟後會變成紅色，<delay8 />真的很美。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這種蝦子棲息於內海，<delay20 />白天潛入沙中，
只露出眼睛，<delay20 />到了晚上才開始活動，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />並以藻類、貝殼或<delay8 />動物的殘骸為食。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="1" />日本囊對蝦<colour id="65535" />和其他蝦子不同，<delay20 />
不會將卵留在腹中，而是直接排至海裡。<delay20 /><pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然產卵數很多，
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但大多淪為其他動物的食物，<delay20 />
能存活下來的少之又少。</message>
	<message label="DiveFish_02848" attrib="00 00 00 00"><colour id="1" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />伊勢龍蝦<colour id="65535" /><delay20 />是大型蝦類的代表。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其略彎的腰間和長長的鬍鬚<delay20 />是長壽的象徵，<delay20 />
在日本常被作為祝賀或過年的裝飾，<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是充滿吉祥寓意的蝦子。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="1" />伊勢龍蝦<colour id="65535" />棲息於淺海岩岸，其天敵為章魚。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為了保護自己，<delay8 />牠時常會在章魚的天敵<delay8 />
「裸胸鱔」附近徘徊。</message>
	<message label="DiveFish_02849" attrib="00 00 00 00"><colour id="1" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />螯龍蝦<colour id="65535" />，<delay8 />也有人稱之為「波士頓龍蝦」。<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />擁有大螯的螯龍蝦是淡水龍蝦的親戚，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />同時也是著名的高級食材。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />體型比一般淡水龍蝦大，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />據說壽命可長達100年以上。<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />抓到<colour id="1" />螯龍蝦<colour id="65535" />後，<delay8 />必須立刻將螯固定住，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />否則具有攻擊性的螯龍蝦可是相當危險的。</message>
	<message label="DiveFish_02850" attrib="00 00 00 00"><colour id="1" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />松葉蟹<colour id="65535" /><delay20 />棲息在深海中，堪稱是冬季味覺之王，<10_4 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其暗紅色的甲殼，<delay20 />經加熱後會變成鮮紅色。<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />壽命約20年，<delay20 />靠著反覆脫皮而生長。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />即使腳斷了，也能在下次脫皮時再長出來。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雌性的體型約為雄性的一半，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />又被稱為「香箱蟹」或<delay8 />「背子蟹」。</message>
	<message label="DiveFish_02852" attrib="00 00 00 00"><colour id="1" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />鱈場蟹<colour id="65535" /><delay8 />其實是寄居蟹的近親。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />由於肉質鮮美，外形和螃蟹相似，<delay20 />
常被誤認為是螃蟹的一種。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然牠的腳，包含鉗子，看起來有八隻，
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但其實甲殼裡面還有兩隻小腳，<delay20 />
所以一共有十隻。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />腳撐開之後，其體型可達一公尺以上，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />較粗的腳裡塞滿了肉，<delay20 /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />口感滿分。</message>
	<message label="DiveFish_02853" attrib="00 00 00 00"><colour id="1" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />高腳蟹<colour id="65535" /><delay8 />最大的特徵就是長長的腳。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />特別是雄性，<delay8 />腳撐開之後，可超過三公尺，<delay20 />
是世界上最大的螃蟹。<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大約從一千萬年前開始，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />高腳蟹就一直生活在深海海底，<delay20 />
外形幾乎沒變過，堪稱是「活化石」。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，外形如此特別的<colour id="1" />高腳蟹<colour id="65535" />，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />吃起來卻沒那麼特別<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
　　　　　　　　　　　　<colour id="5" />※純屬個人感想。<colour id="65535" /></message>
	<message label="DiveFish_02854" attrib="00 00 00 00"><colour id="1" /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />章魚<colour id="65535" />的八隻腳其實是觸手，<delay frames="30" />大大的頭其實是
身體，<delay frames="30" />而真正的頭是在觸手和身體之間，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這種身體構造真是不可思議啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />牠會用柔軟的觸手纏住螃蟹、蝦子或<delay20 />貝類等，
然後再將牠們吃下肚。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />遭受敵人攻擊時，<delay8 />會吐出煙霧狀的墨汁
再趁機逃走，<delay frames="30" />還會配合周遭環境
改變體色<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />簡直就像忍者一樣。</message>
	<message label="DiveFish_02855" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />白色的身體上有細小的黑點，<delay20 />從沙子裡
鑽出來的樣子就好像從花園生長出來的植物，<delay20 />
<colour id="1" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="65535" />因此有了<colour id="1" />花園鰻<colour id="65535" />這個名字。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />牠們會在淺海海底的沙子裡成群築巢，<delay frames="30" />
從沙子裡探出頭來，<delay8 />
吃掉隨潮流而來的浮游生物。<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />由於生性膽小，<delay20 />只要一感受到危險，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就會立刻躲進巢穴中。</message>
	<message label="DiveFish_02856" attrib="00 00 00 00"><colour id="1" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />鸚鵡螺<colour id="65535" />的外形<delay frames="30" />
常會被認為是菊石的後代。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但其實<delay8 />鸚鵡螺比菊石<delay frames="30" />還要早一億多年出現。
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />從鸚鵡螺衍生出來的菊石<delay8 />雖曾繁極一時，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但卻隨著恐龍一起滅絕。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />另外，<colour id="1" />鸚鵡螺<colour id="65535" /><delay20 />幾乎沒有經歷演化，<delay20 />
直到現在仍生活在南太平洋和澳洲近海。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />廣義來說，<colour id="1" />鸚鵡螺<colour id="65535" />算是魷魚和章魚的親戚，<delay20 />
不過卻有多達60～90隻觸手，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />並用來捕食魚貝類的殘骸。</message>
	<message label="DiveFish_02857" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="1" />鱟<colour id="65535" /><delay20 />從恐龍時代就存在了，
且外形幾乎沒變過，<delay20 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />所以有「活化石」之稱。<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒想到「活化石」竟出乎意料地多呢。<size value="75" /><pageBreak /><size value="100" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然外表看起來像是甲殼類的生物，<delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但分類上卻較接近蜘蛛或蠍子。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一般喜歡生活在海邊的泥沙中，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但由於沿岸的開墾和<delay20 />填海造地的關係，<delay20 />
其數量年年銳減<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="DiveFish_02858" attrib="00 00 00 00"><colour id="1" />大王具足蟲<colour id="65535" /><delay8 />棲息於深海中，<delay frames="30" />
體型最大可達50公分，<delay8 />
<anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />跟世界最大的鼠婦是同類。<delay20 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak />外表凶狠又帶點滑稽，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />身形雖圓潤，<delay20 />但游起泳來
卻出乎意料地快。<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />由於食量驚人，<delay20 />能將沉在海底的
動物殘骸吃個精光，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因此又有「深海清道夫」之稱。<pageBreak /><tag a="10" b="12" /><anim id="Shaking" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 /><size value="75" />竟然有50公分，<delay20 />天啊，想到就噁心<tag a="110" b="0" /><size value="100" /></message>
	<message label="DiveFish_06920" attrib="00 00 00 00"><colour id="1" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />螢火魷<colour id="65535" /><delay20 />身長約6公分，<delay8 />
是小型的洄游性魷魚。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />平常生活在深海中，<delay20 />
只有產卵的時候，
才會來到海岸附近。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其最大的特徵是體內有發光器，<delay20 />
能發出藍白色的光。<10_4 /><pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />據說發光的目的<delay frames="30" />是為了<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />威嚇、<delay20 />迷惑敵人、<delay20 />
與同伴溝通<delay20 /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />以及吸引獵物等。</message>
	<message label="DiveFish_07191" attrib="00 00 00 00">比起<colour id="1" />三疣梭子蟹<colour id="65535" />這個名稱，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大家或許更常<delay20 />直接叫牠「梭子蟹」。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />牠的後腳腳尖像蛙鞋一樣，<delay frames="30" />
能在海中<delay8 />自由自在地快速游泳。<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />由於這種螃蟹非常美味，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以自古以來就被人們拿來食用。</message>
	<message label="DiveFish_07203" attrib="00 00 00 00"><colour id="1" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />吸血烏賊<colour id="65535" /><delay20 />在被發現的時候，
因為有八隻腳，<delay20 />所以被認為是章魚。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但後來<delay8 />在隱密的地方，<delay8 />
發現牠還有另外兩隻腳，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />才認定牠為<delay20 />魷魚！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak />牠的學名<delay20 /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />直譯之後，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是「來自地獄的吸血鬼魷魚」的意思<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而更進一步的研究結果顯示，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />牠既不是魷魚也不是章魚。
而是與魷魚和章魚未分化前的祖先<delay20 />較為接近。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />另外，<delay8 />雖然牠外表給人的印象是<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />地獄啊、吸血鬼啊這種<delay8 />
恐怖的感覺，<delay20 />但實際上<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />牠是一種相當溫和的生物，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />會把浮游生物的殘骸、藻類和泥沙等<delay frames="30" />
這些所謂的「海洋雪」聚成丸子形狀來吃。</message>
	<message label="DiveFish_07214" attrib="00 00 00 00"><colour id="1" />大硨磲<colour id="65535" /><delay20 />棲息在溫暖海域的珊瑚礁上，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是世界上最大的雙殼貝類動物。<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />據說殼寬最大可達2公尺，<delay frames="30" />
重量足足可超過300公斤，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而壽命也可高達100年以上。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />除了會過濾海水中的浮游生物來吃之外，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還會讓一種叫做「蟲黃藻」的藻類<delay8 />
住進自己的體內，<delay8 />形成共生關係。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />藻類透過光合作用製造出的糖分和蛋白質，<delay20 />
為大硨磲提供生長的營養。<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要將殼朝上打開一半，<delay20 />
就能補給養分，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是太讓人羨慕了。</message>
	<message label="DiveFish_07228" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />外形有點古怪的<colour id="1" />海鞘<colour id="65535" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實不是貝類或海參的同類，<delay20 />
更不是植物。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而是屬於被囊動物亞門中<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一種會過濾浮游生物來吃的生物。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />幼體時期，有一小段時間<delay20 />會像蝌蚪一樣游泳，
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但沒過多久就會附著在海底的岩石上，<delay20 />
然後就再也不會離開那個地方了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />海鞘有一種獨特的味道和香氣，<delay20 />
喜歡的人很喜歡，
不喜歡的人則是相當討厭。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對喜歡的人來說，<delay20 />那是同時帶有
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />鮮、<delay20 />苦、<delay20 />酸、<delay20 />甜、<delay20 />鹹的滋味，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />令人難以言喻。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過對我來說，<delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />老實講，我不太能接受<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="DiveFish_07245" attrib="00 00 00 00"><colour id="1" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />海月水母<colour id="65535" />是一種常見於日本近海的水母，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對當地人來說並不陌生。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />牠的觸手有毒，<delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />碰到會感到微微刺痛，
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但牠漂浮在海裡樣子卻十分療癒。<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />當海裡營養過剩<delay20 />或海水溫度改變時，
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />海月水母就會大量出現，<delay frames="30" />
對漁業造成損害。<delay20 /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="DiveFish_07252" attrib="00 00 00 00"><colour id="1" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />扁面蛸<colour id="65535" />是一種棲息在深海中，<delay20 />
身長約20公分的小型章魚。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />牠和一般章魚不太一樣，樣子非常扁平，<delay frames="30" />
雖然同樣有八隻腳，<delay8 />但腳和腳之間有膜，<delay20 />
樣子就像降落傘一樣。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="1" />扁面蛸<colour id="65535" />並不是藉由噴水來游泳的，<delay20 />
而是像水母那樣一面漂浮一面游泳，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />並擺動像耳朵一樣的鰭來控制方向。<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那種悠閒自在的感覺，<delay20 />讓人討厭不起來呢。</message>
	<message label="DiveFish_07267" attrib="00 00 00 00"><colour id="1" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />石筆海膽<colour id="65535" />棲息在
印度洋至西太平洋的珊瑚礁上，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />殼徑約6～7公分。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然說到海膽就會聯想到刺，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但<colour id="1" />石筆海膽<colour id="65535" />的刺卻像筆桿一樣，
長得粗粗的，<delay frames="30" /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />頂端也不尖銳。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />跟一般的海膽比起來，怎麼說呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />更有重量感，<delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺可以更紮實地防禦呢。</message>
	<message label="DiveFish_07278" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />自古以來就被人們拿來食用的<colour id="1" />峨螺<colour id="65535" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />廣泛分布於溫帶地區，<delay20 />
通常棲息於水深較淺的泥沙中。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />縱長約6～7公分，<10_4 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />主要以魚的屍體等腐肉為食，<delay20 />
是海洋的清道夫。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="DiveFish_07303" attrib="00 00 00 00"><colour id="1" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />海豬<colour id="65535" /><delay frames="30" /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是一種深海的海參，<delay20 />
生活在水深1000～6000公尺的海底。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />身長約5～10公分，<delay20 />有10幾隻腳，<delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />會一面在海底爬行一面尋找泥沙裡的食物。<pageBreak /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然有人覺得<delay frames="40" /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />牠醜得很可愛<tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但對我來說<delay frames="30" />可是完全不能接受！</message>
	<message label="DiveFish_07308" attrib="00 00 00 00"><colour id="1" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />首長黃道蟹<colour id="65535" /><delay frames="30" /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />又名「鄧傑內斯蟹」，
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />甲殼的形狀<delay8 />如銀杏葉一般呈現扇形。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />棲息於北美西岸，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是最受歡迎的食用蟹。</message>
	<message label="DiveFish_07318" attrib="00 00 00 00"><colour id="1" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />偕老同穴<colour id="65535" /><delay frames="30" /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />又被稱為「維納斯的花籃」，<delay20 />
是一種圓筒狀的海綿。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其玻璃質的<delay20 />二氧化矽網狀骨骼，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />形成了具有玻璃纖維的細緻花籃。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<delay20 /><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是美得讓人神魂顛倒啊～<delay frames="40" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="DiveFish_07411" attrib="00 00 00 00"><colour id="1" />貽貝<colour id="65535" />的繁殖力<delay8 />非常旺盛，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />目前分布於世界各地。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其原產地為地中海，<delay20 />
在歐洲以外的地區<delay8 />都被視為外來種。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想這種雙殼貝類<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大概是<delay20 />世界上最多人吃的吧。</message>
</msbt>